<p><strong>Benoit Stasiaczyk</strong><strong>三重奏</strong><strong>/ </strong><strong>川</strong><strong>. </strong><strong>响</strong><strong>Li Xiaochuan. Sounds</strong></p>
<p>时间：2020.11.22（星期日）SUN. 20:00 / 21:30</p>
